# Documentation rules

## Code

- Add JSDoc comments to public or exported functions.
- Add comments to complex code that explain the why behind the code.- - Keep an `/docs/OVERVIEW.md` file with the tech stack, folder structure, and high-level architecture diagram.
- Keep an `/docs/JOURNAL.md` file with the session chat key actions and decisions.
- Keep an `/README.md` file with info about the project and the dev test workflow